feature/passwd-expire
---------------------

It provides a mechanism to force users to update their passwords when next
serial login by template feature/passwd-expire.

Introduce 2 variables:
* FORCE_PASSWD_EXPIRE:
  The flag whether this feature is enabled, and it should not be disabled.

* FORCE_EXPIRED_USERS:
  It works with EXTRA_USERS_PARAMS which is from extrausers.bbclass. Users set
  in FORCE_EXPIRED_USERS will be promted to update the passwords when next time
  serial login.


#@TYPE: Wrtemplate
#@NAME: passwd-expire
#@DESCRIPTION: Force users to update passwords when next time serial login
